question: Heng-ha̍k ê metrical tit-tio̍h siōng-koân ê NDCG siau-tōaⁿ?
Kènnāi ē Kendall thiaⁿ siáⁿ-chē, hō͘ só͘-ū chū 'αS' khai-sí ê metric lâi phó͘-cha. (Kènnāi ē Kendall thiaⁿ siáⁿ-chē, hō͘ só͘-ū chū 'αS' khai-sí ê metric lâi phó͘-cha.)
Kui mi metric ê Kendall score si siunn siunn kee, in ê Spearman score si siam ah?

Chit kuíⁿ Metrics, tùi αS1 kàu αS4 ê Spearman score ê tâi-tsō· ū sím-mih piàn-huà? Chit ê tâi-tsō· sī ē-tiâu-tiâu (consistently increasing), dâi-tiâu (consistently decreasing), ài-m̄-ài tōa-sió (fluctuating)?
answer: Tùi αS1 kàu αS4 ê Spearman score ê tâi-tsō· sī ē-tiâu-tiâu. Ia̍h-ū ê ta̍t-tiāu tùi αS1 ê 0.39, kàu αS2 ê 0.394, kàu αS3 ê 0.4, tùi-chòe αS4 ê 0.409, múi chi̍t ê hō·-sò· lóng pí chiân chi̍t ê koân.

question: Chiah-chūnn ê tiāu-kiāⁿ tang-tiong, ū hō-chí ê mét-liô ê NDCG siau-piah pí 0.55 koân, chi̍t-pêngNDC K siau-piah pí 0.55 koân, chi̍t-pêng_Kendall siau-piah pí 0.25 koân?
Siaⁿ-chi̍t-ê 'αS' hē-lia̍t ê metric ha̍p-kiat ê Spearman tîm-sò͘ ê chóng-iok-chō͘ chiàm to-sò͘ ê to-sò͘ thiaⁿ-chi̍t-pái, chiáⁿ-chòe pek-hun-táⁿ hām sió-siá nn̄g-ê só͘-chāi ê sòaⁿ.
Ài tiāⁿ, nā-sī 'PSR' metric ê NDCG score hō͘ jīm-hô tōa-khuài kā choán chòe hū-tī 'Sharpe Ratio' ê NDCG score, hit-ê piáⁿ-chhiúⁿ choân-pō͘ metric ê pêng-kin NDCG score ē sī sím-mih?
Tāⁿ-kò͘ ê 'Kendall' kap 'NDCG' nn̄g ki hāng-ba̍k ê koan-hē, ē-sái kám-sek chū nn̄g ki chhòaⁿ ê sî-kan chha-put-to ū tōa-khí ê tùi-chū hē-lu̍t? Chē-chāi chāi su-kì lâi chèng-bêng lí ê koan-tiám.
answer: Ē-sái kám-sek chū 'Kendall' kap 'NDCG' ê tit-hun chi-kan ū tōa-khí ê tùi-chū hē-lu̍t. Chha-put-to sió-sió ê 'Kendall' tit-hun (chāi 'Sharpe Ratio' ê 0.087 kap 'PSR' ê 0.085) mā ū sió-sió ê 'NDCG' tit-hun (0.393 kap 0.388). Kāng-khoán ê kò͘-chāi, chāi nn̄g ki 'αS' hāng-ba̍k, ū chin tōa-khí ê 'Kendall' tit-hun (chāi 0.265 kàu 0.278), mā ū siōng tōa-khí ê 'NDCG' tit-hun (chāi 0.589 kàu 0.636). Chit ê hong-ê piàn-hòa piáu-bêng chāi 'Kendall' tit-hun cheng-ka ê sî, 'NDCG' tit-hun mā chin-chhiūⁿ ē cheng-ka.

question: Tī sann-ê siông-sò͘ lia̍t (Spearman, Kendall, NDCG) tiong, hō-só͘ siōng-tōa kap siōng-sè ê kî-kan le̍k-tōa?

‘Sharpe Ratio’ kah ‘PSR’ chit-ê metric hō͘-chòe-e̍k-ê chi̍p-thôan, pí ‘αS’ chit-ê metric tī-lâi khah-kē-ê siaⁿ. Nā-sī ài kiâⁿ ‘Spearman’, ‘Kendall’, `NDCG` chit saⁿ-ê hē-sòan hong-sek tiong, siáⁿ-chi̍t-ê ê su-iáⁿ (absolute difference) chhú-tiong-ê (|average score of the low group| kah |average score of the high group|) siāng-tōa?
Lai-e metric chi-sī tōa kán-ná Kendall correlation siōng-kè khuí ê?
